race.description: Become A Brc Member Qtis 3YO Handicap
race.comment: The penny has dropped for VOODOO LASS (2) who has put back-to-back victories together over this distance range and looks very well-placed in this line-up. Gets the services of Maloney in the irons and can bring up the hat-trick without surprising. HA'PENNY HATCH (1) is a winner over this track and trip and should be ready to peak now third-up from the break. Looms as the main danger. QUEEN JEDDAH (7) has just run into one better in both starts to date and looks the be building up to a maiden win. Expect a positive performance. WORTHY ENUFF (5) gets in well at the weights with the 3kg claim and may earn some minor money. SWEET PRETENDER (4) next in line.
